{"tid":1419354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍如進擊香港，梁天琦會非常危險","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:37.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53b3c24244bd1b5a68263c7ef59e76af4400b7f7","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:58:24.000Z","msg":"如果解放軍入香港，代表香港實行一國一制<br />\n走到既人就好彩， 走唔到既人會有排受。<br />\n<br />\n最危險既， 係坐緊監既政治犯， 因為佢地走唔到。<br />\n梁天琦同美國隊長呢d政治重犯， 可能更危險。終身監禁大有可能； 唔好彩既， 分分鐘會無條命。<br />\n<br />\n（唔好唔記得，老共已經痴撚左線。有線訪問李旺陽後，李旺陽立即被自殺。）<br />\n<br />\n好似陶傑呢類人唔想焦土， 唔係因為無膽， 只係唔想見到更多義士受苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2231ca29d72bffe4289a5ecba152c84bd51388","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"陶傑: 林鄭與董建華要引解放軍入香港. 示威者不需再犯法, 不要中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417111/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417111/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1147e73e2a26f5b977c3b55db01d23690fa6f2a0","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a933c3494b6e00093f0758b451df8710386f8a","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"2f2c71ed9007eb432db4945fdef86994f0be0657","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5965f939314cbd680a293fc856a8ef7b244c304","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"不可以將義士當condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e0241717a0a1ec5aeeacfb30be0860f86a4579","tid":1419354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":